 Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34191,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/05\/22\/umar-beware-mockery\/","url_meta":{"origin":21313,"position":3},"title":"Umar II on Mockery: Beware of making fun and causing hatred","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 22, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mawardi reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBeware of mockery, for it is foolishness that produces malice.\u201d Some of the wise men said, \u201cIndeed, mockery is a form of insult, unless it makes the recipient laugh.\u201d And it is said, \"Mockery is only named\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18878,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/04\/20\/umar-no-killing-civilians\/","url_meta":{"origin":21313,"position":4},"title":"Umar II on War: No killing women, children, civilians, non-combatants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Yahya ibn Yahya reported: I wrote to Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, asking him about the verse, \u201cFight in the way of Allah those who fight you, but do not transgress,\u201d (2:190). Umar wrote back to me, saying, \u201cThis refers to women, children, and whoever\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0